PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,FSix coins and tokens dating back to
OL,8,Fthe 19th century have been discovered
OL,9,Fbeneath the foremast of HMS Victory
OL,10,Fafter the masts were removed in the
OL,11,Flatest stage of a 10-year, #42 million
OL,12,Frestoration project.
OL,14,FA 750-tonne crane was used to remove
OL,15,Fthe mizzen (rear), foremast (front)
OL,16,Fand bowsprit (the bow) masts from Vice-
OL,17,FAdmiral Lord Nelson's flagship at
OL,18,FPortsmouth Historic Dockyard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,FAfter their removal, conservationists
OL,8,Ffound the coins which had been placed
OL,9,Funder the foremast as part of a
OL,10,Ftradition to bring good fortune to the
OL,11,Fvessel and crew.
OL,13,FAndrew Baines, executive director of
OL,14,Fmuseum operations at Royal Navy
OL,15,FMuseums, said: "We are incredibly
OL,16,Fexcited to have discovered six coins
OL,17,Fbeneath the fore lower mast of HMS
OL,18,FVictory.
OL,26,@wD@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,F"This find connects us directly to a
OL,8,Fmaritime tradition stretching back
OL,9,Fthousands of years.
OL,11,F"The placing of coins beneath a ship's
OL,12,Fmast has long been seen as a symbolic
OL,13,Fact, often associated with protection
OL,14,Fand good fortune for the vessel and
OL,15,Fher crew.
OL,17,F"Following the earlier discovery of a
OL,18,Fsingle farthing beneath the main lower
OL,19,Fmast, we had hoped there might be
OL,20,Fsomething similar beneath the foremast.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,F"But to uncover six coins was an
OL,8,Fextraordinary surprise."
OL,10,FFive of the coins date to the period
OL,11,Fwhen the foremast was stepped in 1894,
OL,12,Fwhen the ship's original wooden masts
OL,13,Fwere replaced with wrought iron
OL,14,Fversions.
OL,16,FThe sixth coin has been identified as
OL,17,Fa token from Prince Edward Island,
OL,18,FCanada, dated to 1835 with an image of
OL,19,Fa ship stamped on it.
OL,26,@pD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,FMr Baines said: "The 1835 Prince
OL,8,FEdward Island token is one of the most
OL,9,Fintriguing finds. Its inscription,
OL,10,F'Ships, Colonies and Commerce' ` a
OL,11,Fslogan closely associated with the
OL,12,Fmaritime and imperial trade networks
OL,13,Fof the 19th century ` reflects the
OL,14,Fworld in which HMS Victory served and
OL,15,Fsuggests these coins may have been
OL,16,Fchosen for symbolic as well as
OL,17,Fpractical reasons.
OL,26,@oD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,F"We cannot yet say why this particular
OL,8,Ftoken was selected, but its presence
OL,9,Fbeneath the foremast adds another
OL,10,Flayer to the story.
OL,12,F"Hidden from view for more than a
OL,13,Fcentury, these objects nevertheless
OL,14,Fspeak directly to the people who cared
OL,15,Ffor Victory and the traditions they
OL,16,Fchose to continue."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,FKaroline Sofie Hennum, conservator on
OL,8,FHMS Victory, said that all of the
OL,9,Fcoins had been heavily degraded from
OL,10,Fthe prolonged pressure of the 50
OL,11,Ftonnes of mast, along with corrosion
OL,12,Ffrom the 132 years since they were
OL,13,Fplaced there.
OL,15,FShe said: "To unlock the secrets of
OL,16,Fthe coins covered up by decades of
OL,17,Fcorrosion, they needed to be removed
OL,18,Ffrom the base plate, cleaned and X-
OL,19,Frayed.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,F"Luckily, overall, the condition of
OL,8,Fthe coins was good, and they came away
OL,9,Ffrom the base easily.
OL,11,F"Then using a microscope, we carefully
OL,12,Fcleaned them with brushes, wooden
OL,13,Fskewers and tweezers, bringing more
OL,14,Finformation to light.
OL,16,F"Finally, using a technique called X-
OL,17,Fradiography, we could see beneath the
OL,18,Fcorrosion revealing both sides of the
OL,19,Fcoin in one image."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,FThe five coins are three one penny
OL,8,Fpieces featuring a "bun head" portrait
OL,9,Fof Queen Victoria, two of which dated
OL,10,Fto 1890 and one to 1892, with a
OL,11,Fhalfpenny dated to 1890, along with a
OL,12,Ffarthing dated to 1882.
OL,14,FThey will go on display from May 23 in
OL,15,Fthe Victory Gallery at Portsmouth
OL,16,FHistoric Dockyard.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
