OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779354383
OL,3,CSix 19th century coins found placed
OL,4,Cunder HMS Victory's mast for 'good
OL,5,Cfortune'
OL,7,FHMS Victory, which is the world's
OL,8,Foldest commissioned warship, was
OL,9,FNelson's flagship at the Battle of
OL,10,FTrafalgar and it was on the ship's
OL,11,Fquarterdeck that he was fatally shot
OL,12,Fby a French sniper on October 21 1805.
OL,14,FVictory was first floated out at
OL,15,FChatham in 1765 but by the 1920s was
OL,16,Fin poor condition and moved to dry
OL,17,Fdock in Portsmouth in 1922.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
